title: Bonus Episode - 2Chainz Talks Funny Lyrics + Uber Incident
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
2 Chainz joined Ebro in the Morning fresh out of hanging out with Ye, Fabolous, Dave East in the studio, to have a great conversation about his music, business ventures, and being considered one of the best in hip hop! He also discusses his accomplishments, his different restaurants, the uber incident involving his wife and kids, and breaks down some of our favorite lyrics! 'Dope Don’t Sell Itself' is out now! #EbrointheMorning#HOT97#2Chainz
